<div class="ja">
<svg viewBox="0 0 700 340" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="26" fill="#fafafa" font-size="13" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">ポジションサイズごとの破産確率(対数スケール)</text>
  <text x="20" y="42" fill="#71717a" font-size="10" font-family="sans-serif">前提:勝率55%、損益比1:1・R=(q/p)^N・概念図</text>
  <rect x="325.56" y="50" width="294.44" height="220" fill="#f87171" opacity="0.08"/>
  <text x="472.78" y="63" fill="#f87171" font-size="10" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif" font-weight="700">高リスク領域</text>
  <line x1="90" y1="138" x2="620" y2="138" stroke="#71717a" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
